om a sitting or recumbent position and to notify their doctor if they experience dizziness, lightheadedness, syncope, orthostasis, or tachycardia.', 'Synergism', NULL, NULL, 'Moderate', NULL, 'DDInter', 'pharmacodynamic', 1767317476);
